</div>";s:7:"options";O:8:"stdClass":6:{s:15:"original_author";s:68:"iaminawe - design, animation and illustration from the tip of Africa";s:9:"timestamp";i:1226772907;s:12:"original_url";s:53:"http://ak22.iaminawe.com/2008/11/15/breaking-the-ice/";s:4:"guid";s:53:"http://ak22.iaminawe.com/2008/11/15/breaking-the-ice/";s:4:"tags";a:10:{i:0;s:9:"Animation";i:1;s:4:"News";i:2;s:7:"Theatre";i:3;s:3:"Web";i:4;s:10:"animations";i:5;s:6:"aurora";i:6;s:9:"Cape-Town";i:7;s:6:"drupal";i:8;s:10:"muizenberg";i:9;s:9:"wordpress";}s:7:"domains";a:0:{}}}i:1;O:8:"stdClass":3:{s:5:"title";s:31:"Artskinz - tight, smooth, tough";s:11:"description";s:4640:"<h2 align="center"></h2>
<p style="text-align: center"><img src="http://ak22.iaminawe.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/04/artskinzid.jpg" alt="artskinzid.jpg" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://ak22.iaminawe.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/07/artskinz4.jpg" title="artskinz4.jpg" rel="lightbox[as]"><img src="http://ak22.iaminawe.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/07/artskinz4.thumbnail.jpg" alt="artskinz4.jpg" /></a><a href="http://ak22.iaminawe.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/07/artskinz2.jpg" title="artskinz2.jpg" rel="lightbox[as]"><img src="http://ak22.iaminawe.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/07/artskinz2.thumbnail.jpg" alt="artskinz2.jpg" /></a><a href="http://ak22.iaminawe.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/07/artskinz3.jpg" title="artskinz3.jpg" rel="lightbox[as]"><img src="http://ak22.iaminawe.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/07/artskinz3.thumbnail.jpg" alt="artskinz3.jpg" /></a></p>
<h2 align="center"><strike>www.artskinz.co.za</strike></h2>
<p><em>Unfortunately this site is no longer live as Artskinz had to shut up shop. I will move it over onto a test server at some point but until then this link is unavailable to look at. Sorry. </em></p>
<p>Iaminawe recently created the website and identity for new startup, Artskinz,  which manufactures high quality protective and stylish vinyl covers for your i-pod&#8217;s and laptops.</p>
<p>The designs for the skins are cherry picked from a range of Cape Town&#8217;s  hottest illustrators and fine artists including superheroes like Kronk, The Black Heart Gang, Mine Jonker, Love and Hate Collective, Carmen Ziervogel, Rick Treweek, Mikey Staal and host of other talent. There are also designs from underground graffitti maniacs Faith 47, Senyol, Warren Lewis and Wealz 130 with new designs and artists being added all the time.</p>
<p>The site was created by integrating <a href="http://www.oscommerce.org/" target="_blank">OSCommerce</a> with <a href="http://www.wordpress.org" target="_blank">Wordpress</a> to create an online shop with blog attached. I won&#8217;t go so far as to say the integration was a painless one and I found trying to skin OScommerce effectively to be very tricky.</p>
<p>We have a few designs in the range with more coming soon. Check them out and click to order any of the designs or see larger versions.</p>
<p align="center"><a href="http://artskinz.co.za/catalog/product_info.php?manufacturers_id=10=iaminawe&amp;products_id=39" target="_blank"><img src="http://artskinz.co.za/catalog/product_thumb.php?img=images/ipod_vid_iaminawe_butterflauge.jpg&amp;w=242&amp;h=200" height="181" width="218" /></a><a href="http://artskinz.co.za/catalog/product_info.php?manufacturers_id=10=iaminawe&amp;products_id=37" target="_blank"><img src="http://artskinz.co.za/catalog/product_thumb.php?img=images/ipod_vid_iaminawe_greentealady.jpg&amp;w=242&amp;h=200" height="180" width="219" /></a></p>
<p align="center"><a href="http://artskinz.co.za/catalog/product_info.php?manufacturers_id=10&amp;products_id=31" target="_blank"><img src="http://artskinz.co.za/catalog/product_thumb.php?img=images/laptop_iaminawe_tealady.jpg&amp;w=261&amp;h=200" height="214" width="281" /></a></p>
<p align="left">These designs came from our range of <a href="http://ak22.iaminawe.com/2007/01/10/cityflauge-t-shirts/">Cityflauge T-shirts</a> so we have full cityflauge uniforms now <img src='http://ak22.iaminawe.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif' alt=':)' class='wp-smiley' /> </p>
