<p>The banners and tablecloth were for this years packed Old Mutual Summer Sunset Concert gig at Kirstenbosch which saw about 6000 people packing this beautiful park in Cape Town and dancing the day away with Dom and Dave and special guest artists <strong>Sakhile, Tony Paco, Wayne Bosch, Monique and Max Vidima.</strong></p>
<p>I didnt <a href="http://ak22.iaminawe.com/2006/12/05/kirstenbosch-goldfish-vj/" target="_blank">VJ for the fish</a> this year and a matrix of LED lights replaced the matrix of LCD Flatscreens we had last time but we were stoked to see the new artwork huge on stage in Ross Helliers awesome photos some of which are showcased below.</p>

<object	type="application/x-shockwave-flash"
			data="http://ak22.iaminawe.com/wp-content/themes/default/swf/ssp_slideshowthumbs.swf?xmlfile="http://ak22.iaminawe.com/ssp_director/images.php?album=7""
			width="475"
			height="389">
