</object>
<p>To read more about this gig check out <a href="http://blog.myspace.com/index.cfm?fuseaction=blog.view&amp;friendID=66305370&amp;blogID=366023854" target="_blank">Goldfishes myspace blog</a> on the kirstenbosch party . For more <a href="http://www.facebook.com/album.php?aid=42364&amp;l=7264c&amp;id=586210308" target="_blank">photos on facebook</a> and <a href="http://www.facebook.com/album.php?aid=108315&amp;id=906705649&amp;ref=mf" target="_blank">over here </a></p>
<p>And of course visit the fish at the site we designed for them at <a href="http://www.goldfishlive.com" target="_blank">www.goldfishlive.com</a></p>
